PrecisAppointment of LINDA ANNE LUSBY, of Wolfville, Nova Scotia, as a member of the Standards Council of Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years; and designation of LINDA ANNE LUSBY as Chairperson of the Standards Council of Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Richard Lafontaine, whose term has expired, effective April 4, 1998.
